1. Kada *oseti* miris hrane, pas će odmah početi da laje. (When he *senses* the smell of food, the dog will start barking immediately.)

2. Zbog hladnoće, počela je da *oseti* trnce u prstima. (Due to the cold, she began to *feel* tingling in her fingers.)

3. *Osetio* sam olakšanje kada sam saznao da je sve u redu. (I *felt* relieved when I found out everything was okay.)

4. Ona je veoma emotivna i često *oseća* preteranu tugu. (She is very emotional and often *feels* excessive sadness.)

5. Mogu *osećati* bol u leđima već nekoliko dana. (I can *feel* the pain in my back for several days now.)

6. Kada je video svoju baku, osetio je nostalgiju za svojim detinjstvom. (When he saw his grandma, he *felt* nostalgia for his childhood.)

7. Prijatno *osećanje* sunčevih zraka na koži probudilo je u meni sreću. (The pleasant *feeling* of sun rays on the skin awakened happiness in me.)

8. *Osetljiv* sam na buku i ne volim kada je glasno. (I am *sensitive* to noise and don't like it when it's loud.)

9. Moja prijateljica ima neverovatno dobar *osećaj* za modu. (My friend has an incredible sense of fashion.)

10. Nije u redu *osećati* zavist prema drugima zbog nečega što nemate. (It's not okay to *feel* envy towards others for something you don't have.)